membershipTypes.name: Cinecard Membership
membershipTypes.description:
Support the work of Glasgow Film, a registered charity, with a 365-day membership that includes:

  • 4 free standard-priced cinema tickets
  • £1.50 off standard GFT screenings, Friday bargain matinees and Tuesday Treats
  • 3-month subscription to online film streaming service MUBI (for first-time MUBI subscribers)
  • £2.50 off NT Live / live event screenings
  • Earn loyalty points for every £1 spent on Glasgow Film tickets that can be redeemed for GFT standard-priced tickets
  • Exclusive previews screenings

membershipTypes.name: 15-25 Card
membershipTypes.description:
Our free 15-25 Card is the must-have membership for Glaswegian film fans.

Our members enjoy the following benefits:

·      £6 tickets for standard GFT screenings and discounted tickets for standard Glasgow Film Festival screenings

·      Access to one free youth screening each month

·      Earn loyalty points for every pound you spend on Glasgow Film tickets

·      3-month subscription to online film streaming service MUBI (for first-time MUBI subscribers)

membershipTypes.name: Cinecard+ Membership
membershipTypes.description:
Support the work of Glasgow Film, a registered charity with an annual membership that includes:

  • 4 free standard-priced cinema tickets
  • £1.50 off standard GFT screenings, Friday bargain matinees and Tuesday Treats
  • 3-month subscription to online film streaming service MUBI (for first-time MUBI subscribers)
  • £2.50 off NT Live / live event screenings
  • Earn loyalty points for every £1 spent on Glasgow Film tickets that can be redeemed for GFT standard-priced tickets
  • Exclusive previews screenings

membershipTypes.name: Glasgow Film Employee Membership
membershipTypes.description:
• Unlimited personal tickets - limited to one per screening - for standard-priced performances, excluding Free List Suspended performances
  • 2 guest tickets per month, valid for standard-priced performances, excluding Free List Suspended performances 
  • Discounted paid tickets once all complimentary tickets have been used or for FLS screenings.
